@node INTROE "Introduction"

    Long, long ago, when the Directory Opus was only of version of 4.12, and I
 was  barely  went on Amiga, I was very lazy to tyme in the archive name, when
 creating it, and that's why I invented the new method, which allows to create
 archives with the only one mouseclick. Time passed, DOpus changed on my eyes,
 and became of the 5-th version, and  here  my  already  calmed  lazyness  was
 seriously  shocked.  The  point  is  that  the  creators of this masterpiece,
 probably haven't thought about the guys like me. Though all  my  attempts  of
 converting configs of AutoLHA(LZX) failed. The cause was very simple -somehow
 the mask {Ou} became not working at all.( It is not working now too ).  After
 the  long  "fight" with my lazyness this program was created, which, I think,
 will help you to pack anything easier. However this is not the only thing  it
 can do.

@endnode
